---------------------------
Fantastic Maps
---------------------------

This App is for business owners.
It allows them to visually fill relevant business data with the help of a map.

More importantly, it allows them to analyze the data visually and also allows them to make location based query visually. i.e. they can draw lines


---------------------------
APIs Used
---------------------------
Yahoo Maps
YUI Charts



---------------------------
DevStack
---------------------------

Ruby    ---- Language
Sinatra ---- Framework
Mongodb ---- Database
Haml    ---- Html Goodness
Heroku  ---- Hosting
Code    ---- git://github.com/kgthegreat/fantastic-maps.git
URL     ---- http://fantasticmaps.heroku.com/